\phi(t)\ :=\ f(t\, x)\qquad(0\leq t\leq 1)\ .
f(x)=\phi(1)=\phi(0)+\int_0^1 \phi'(t)\, 1\ dt =\phi(0)+\phi'(t)(t-1)\Bigr|_0^1\ +\int_0^1 \phi''(t)\,(1-t)\ dt\ .
\phi'(t)=\sum_i x_i\ f_{.i}(t\,x) \ ;
\phi''(t)=\sum_i x_i{\partial\over\partial t}f_{.i}(t\,x) =\sum_{i\,k} x_i\,x_k\, f_{.ik}(t\, x)\ .
